name: alphAI
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

The following token has a variable tax function on the smart contract to change tax rates post deployment.
Do your own research and be careful if you are trading this token.

description.en:
alphAI is the fully autonomous AI made to scan the blockchain for alpha.

alphAI is the fully autonomous AI made to scan the blockchain for alpha, notifying you before anyone else knows!


How it Works
The ai scans the blockchain for deployed contracts then has certain parameters indicating if it is an alpha launch or not.

alphAI is a virtuous circle purposed specifically for those investors who deserve appreciation for holding long-term like Chads of the Ethereum Network. A community utility token; by the community and back to the community with trust.

Developers or the team do not hold any tokens for themselves and instead participate with every other investor alike.

3% Tax on Buy
3% Tax on Sell
